	â€¢ Sql statements types :-
		a. DML - Data Manipulation Language
			i. SELECT
			ii. INSERT
			iii. UPDATE
			iv. DELETE
			v. MERGE
		b. DDL - Data Definition Language
			i. CREATE
			ii. ALTER
			iii. DROP
			iv. RENAME
			v. TRUNCTE
			vi. COMMENT
		c. DCL - Data Control language
			i. GRANT
			ii. REVOKE
		d. Transaction Control language
			i. COMMIT
			ii. ROLLBACK
			iii. SAVEPOINT
			
